description: Gets details on a table bucket. For more information, see Viewing details about an Amazon S3 table bucket in the Amazon Simple Storage Service User Guide. You must have the s3tables:GetTableBucket permission to use this operation.

parameters.name: tableBucketARN
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the table bucket.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the table bucket.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the table bucket.

nested_items.name: ownerAccountId
nested_items.description: The ID of the account that owns the table bucket.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The date and time the table bucket was created.

nested_items.name: tableBucketId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of the table bucket.
